		{"id":"cc401357aa91857a","type":"text","text":"Other, the other and another的用法","x":609,"y":399,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"87612a5603f4ae03","type":"text","text":"Who-誰，問人\nWhat-什麼-事情\nWhen-時間\nWhere-地點\nHow-如何(會搭配其他名詞)","x":660,"y":69,"width":285,"height":165},
		{"id":"9a12cccc7b37fbbf","type":"text","text":"BeV 和 一般動詞(Do/Does)","x":195,"y":-348,"width":250,"height":56},
		{"id":"dd1a7ce6d1b5c970","type":"text","text":"肯定句，否定句，疑問句\n其中，否定句和疑問句，出現助動詞後面接V.R.","x":680,"y":-380,"width":250,"height":86},
		{"id":"e588ba690646120d","type":"text","text":"疑問詞要倒裝，把動詞或BeV和Do/Does搬到前面，然後原文照寫。","x":996,"y":-429,"width":250,"height":86},
		{"id":"2305c584fb8a8cc5","type":"text","text":"名詞的規則變化\n直接+s","x":976,"y":212,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"fe6a2ca3059f52e3","type":"text","text":"名詞的不規則變化\nman-men","x":976,"y":332,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"620b0476bb2e4384","x":1060,"y":79,"width":420,"height":101,"color":"2","type":"text","text":"【現在分詞和過去分詞】\nV-ing，正在進行的、非人的(形容非人)、\nV-p.p. 已經完成的，使人..的(形容人)"},
		{"id":"1b31c0088c0b3da7","x":33,"y":484,"width":392,"height":146,"type":"text","text":"【時間介係詞in、on、at】\nin+ 一天以上的時間，或是年、月、季節 eg. in 2024, in Summer\non+特定的日子 eg. I work to go\nat + 時間點，eg. I wake up at 7:00 a.m"},
		{"id":"67529f4fbec58c80","x":458,"y":113,"width":250,"height":60,"type":"text","text":"【表過去習慣Used to】\n句型：Uesd to + V.R.\nE"}
